name floatflt
category Package
revision 77682
shortdesc Wrap text around floats
longdesc The package can float text around figures and tables which do
longdesc not span the full width of a page; it improves upon floatfig,
longdesc and allows tables/figures to be set left/right or alternating
longdesc on even/odd pages.
